caption.text:
I want to share some of experiences that I gain while trying to increase running distance for the past months.

Well actually I'm not the person that love running so much, but I'm the one who keeps trying to be healthy in many ways not limited to running. And I put running as enough as healthy habbit.

First thing will happen to body when you run further is pain. The pain is real, every time you beat your furthest distance. The body tells you've reached new level and ready to take more "kind of load" in the future. When you run further, you'll have long enough time for yourself. Like any other time it could be anything, but for me it's time to refresh my mind. And as many exercises you do, when you run further, it keeps you healthy.

Anything else? I never thought this will be something I'll get when I run further.

I believe mind takes important role not only to body but also in life. And something great doesn't come from smooth conditions. It must be trained in extreme condition and face unpredictable conditions, not only once, but repetitions. And running further somehow provide the conditions. Not only physical, but spiritual. Not only the body, but the mind.

Thanks for reading all along!
Hope it will be positive gesture in many ways.
Last, I would recommend run a marathon as once in lifetime experience.
Happy weekend!

#run #running #marathon #healthy #habit #hokaoneone #longrun #instarun

Terbang.

Kata yang memiliki arti melayang di udara, yang merepresentasikan kebebasan, dan kadang juga diasosiasikan dengan kebahagiaan. Kata ini pun sangat dekat kaitannya dengan langit, burung, dan juga pesawat udara.

Terbang pun dapat menjadi satu bukti di mana kebebasan untuk bermimpi dimiliki oleh semua orang. Wilbur dan Orville Wright yang mulai membuka bengkel sepeda di tahun 1893 sampai pada ide menciptakan teknologi untuk terbang. Dalam kurun waktu 4 tahun (1900-1903) mereka berhasil merealisasikan ide tersebut.

Memang sebenarnya lari tidak sama dengan terbang. Lari adalah melangkah dengan cepat. Namun, di setiap langkah tersebut ada keadaan "melayang di udara" yang sangat singkat.
